<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 07 Sep 2024 18:10:02 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>随着数字影子战争的加剧，以色列军队高层成为错误信息的焦点</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-09-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/as-digital-shadow-war-intensifies-israeli-army-brass-is-in-misinformation-crosshairs/00000191-ccaf-d214-a393-cdbfa9210000</link><description>亲巴勒斯坦的账户发起了一场心理战运动，为巴勒斯坦人提供了短暂的胜利形象，声称以色列国防军高级军官死亡。研究人员将这些错误信息活动追溯到俄罗斯</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Sep 2024 17:44:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-09-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/as-digital-shadow-war-intensifies-israeli-army-brass-is-in-misinformation-crosshairs/00000191-ccaf-d214-a393-cdbfa9210000</guid></item><item><title>以色列处于战争状态，第 337 天：中央情报局局长表示停火协议“最终是一个政治意愿问题”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-07/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-337-cia-chief-says-cease-fire-deal-is-a-question-of-political-will/00000191-cd4e-d214-a393-cdfe57c90000</link><description>纽约时报：哈马斯对人质/停火协议提出了新要求 ■ 加沙医务人员：以色列国防军的袭击在 48 小时内造成至少 61 人死亡 ■ 巴勒斯坦卫生部：以色列国防军在约旦河西岸中部开火，造成 13 岁女孩死亡 ■ 英国军情六处负责人: 伊朗仍计划对哈马斯领导人哈尼亚被杀事件进行报复 ■ 战争已过去 337 天，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Sep 2024 17:20:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-07/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-337-cia-chief-says-cease-fire-deal-is-a-question-of-political-will/00000191-cd4e-d214-a393-cdfe57c90000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡“在他的联盟的祭坛上牺牲了我的兄弟”：以色列人抗议人质释放协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-07/ty-article/.premium/a-week-of-protests-israelis-take-to-the-streets-to-demand-netanyahu-make-a-hostage-deal/00000191-cd22-deaf-a1f1-cdb7ed5e0000</link><description>在从加沙地带打捞出六名人质尸体后，本周每晚都会发生抗议活动。一名人质的母亲说：“只要内塔尼亚胡掌权，我们就会继续把人质装进裹尸袋”</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Sep 2024 16:21:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-07/ty-article/.premium/a-week-of-protests-israelis-take-to-the-streets-to-demand-netanyahu-make-a-hostage-deal/00000191-cd22-deaf-a1f1-cdb7ed5e0000</guid></item><item><title>《国土报》摄影师拍摄的以色列一周</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israels-week-in-pictures-by-haaretz-photographers/00000191-cccc-deaf-a1f1-cdff7af80000</link><description></description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Sep 2024 15:34:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israels-week-in-pictures-by-haaretz-photographers/00000191-cccc-deaf-a1f1-cdff7af80000</guid></item><item><title>涉嫌向本格维尔扔沙子的女子被关押过夜</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-07/ty-article/.premium/woman-suspected-of-throwing-sand-at-ben-gvir-held-in-jail-overnight/00000191-cbc4-d359-a5f9-dfed93970000</link><description>地方法院接受了警方的说法，即如果嫌疑人被释放，调查可能会受到影响。嫌疑人的母亲在X上写道：“独裁警察决定危及我患有慢性疾病的女儿的生命”</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Sep 2024 09:47:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-07/ty-article/.premium/woman-suspected-of-throwing-sand-at-ben-gvir-held-in-jail-overnight/00000191-cbc4-d359-a5f9-dfed93970000</guid></item><item><title>以色列狱警拍摄虐待被拘留者的视频；监狱部门称这是一次“例行演习”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-guards-filmed-abusing-detainees-prison-service-says-its-a-routine-exercise/00000191-cb71-d359-a5f9-dffd26f60000</link><description>《国土报》获得的照片和视频显示，数十名被拘留者戴着手铐趴在地上，其中一些人赤身裸体，一只看门狗在他们上方狂吠。监狱内没有发生任何异常事件促使狱警采取行动</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Sep 2024 08:24:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-guards-filmed-abusing-detainees-prison-service-says-its-a-routine-exercise/00000191-cb71-d359-a5f9-dffd26f60000</guid></item><item><title>报道：三名救援人员在以色列对黎巴嫩的袭击中丧生；以色列北部的无人机警报</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-06/ty-article-live/palestinians-idf-gunfire-kills-13-year-old-girl-in-west-bank-following-settler-clashes/00000191-c8fb-d74e-aff9-ccffedac0000</link><description>中央情报局局长：致力于以色列与哈马斯停火协议，这是一个政治意愿问题 ■ 以色列国防军瞄准加沙学校设立的哈马斯指挥中心的恐怖分子；巴勒斯坦报告：4 人死亡、25 人受伤 ■ 巴勒斯坦司机在约旦河西岸撞上警车后被捕；无人员伤亡 ■ 由于对来自黎巴嫩的火箭弹和无人机的恐惧加剧，以色列北部一些社区的居民被指示留在避难所附近</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 20:56:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-06/ty-article-live/palestinians-idf-gunfire-kills-13-year-old-girl-in-west-bank-following-settler-clashes/00000191-c8fb-d74e-aff9-ccffedac0000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦人：定居者冲突后，以色列军队在约旦河西岸开枪打死 13 岁女孩</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-06/ty-article/palestinians-idf-gunfire-kills-13-year-old-girl-in-west-bank-following-settler-clashes/00000191-c8ea-d12d-a191-fbfa0ec60000</link><description>这名 13 岁女孩的父亲说，她是在家里的房间里被袭击的。目击者称，枪击事件发生前，定居者与以色列国防军爆发了冲突，定居者投掷石块并放火焚烧田地。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 20:02:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-06/ty-article/palestinians-idf-gunfire-kills-13-year-old-girl-in-west-bank-following-settler-clashes/00000191-c8ea-d12d-a191-fbfa0ec60000</guid></item><item><title>甘茨和艾森科特对抗内塔尼亚胡，但很难击败骗子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-09-06/ty-article-opinion/.premium/gantz-and-eisenkot-take-on-netanyahu-but-its-hard-to-beat-a-crook/00000191-c81b-d12d-a191-fb1b12860000</link><description></description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 18:13:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-09-06/ty-article-opinion/.premium/gantz-and-eisenkot-take-on-netanyahu-but-its-hard-to-beat-a-crook/00000191-c81b-d12d-a191-fb1b12860000</guid></item><item><title>由于对以色列国家监督机构缺乏信心，爆炸性的加沙战争报告被束之高阁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-06/ty-article/.premium/lack-of-faith-in-israels-watchdog-leaves-explosive-gaza-war-reports-in-the-drawer/00000191-c773-d4f1-adb7-dff787f80000</link><description>军方认为，战时的批评可能会削弱其表现，司法部长也同意这一点。更重要的是，国家审计长马塔尼亚胡·恩格尔曼被视为本杰明·内塔尼亚胡的傀儡，他热衷于将自己的缺点归咎于他人</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 18:13:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-06/ty-article/.premium/lack-of-faith-in-israels-watchdog-leaves-explosive-gaza-war-reports-in-the-drawer/00000191-c773-d4f1-adb7-dff787f80000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战事第 336 天：联合国称加沙人道主义局势“超出灾难性”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-06/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-336-un-says-humanitarian-situation-in-gaza-beyond-catastrophic/00000191-c7e8-d12d-a191-fff8a74b0000</link><description>布林肯表示，加沙休战条款已达成近 90%，调解员将在未来几天内向以色列和哈马斯提出新建议 ■ 哈马斯发布被谋杀的以色列裔美国人质赫什·戈德堡-波林的视频 ■ 据报道，以色列军队枪杀了美国人- 约旦河西岸抗议活动中的土耳其人权活动家 ■ 这是战争开始 336 天后您需要了解的信息</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 16:06:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-06/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-336-un-says-humanitarian-situation-in-gaza-beyond-catastrophic/00000191-c7e8-d12d-a191-fff8a74b0000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦人：美国土耳其活动家在约旦河西岸被以色列军队枪杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-06/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-reports-american-turkish-activist-shot-dead-by-israeli-soldiers-in-west-bank/00000191-c7f1-df27-a9b9-fffb3dab0000</link><description>该活动人士参加了贝塔的示威活动，自 2021 年定居者埃维亚塔尔前哨基地在贝塔建立以来，该活动每周都会举行。以色列国防军表示，它向一名向士兵投掷石块的人开枪，并正在调查这一事件</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 15:55:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-06/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-reports-american-turkish-activist-shot-dead-by-israeli-soldiers-in-west-bank/00000191-c7f1-df27-a9b9-fffb3dab0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列总检察长告诉最高法院，允许内塔尼亚胡亲自挑选公务员局长是非法的</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-06/ty-article/.premium/allowing-netanyahu-to-handpick-civil-service-chief-is-illegal-ag-tells-top-court/00000191-c79d-dd1b-a7db-f7df3f0d0000</link><description>总检察长要求法院暂停内阁的决定，称这可能会使专员依赖总理而不是公众</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 15:28:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-06/ty-article/.premium/allowing-netanyahu-to-handpick-civil-service-chief-is-illegal-ag-tells-top-court/00000191-c79d-dd1b-a7db-f7df3f0d0000</guid></item><item><title>两名贝都因以色列人说，以色列国防军士兵在他们在约旦河西岸开车时殴打了他们</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-06/ty-article/.premium/two-bedouin-israelis-say-idf-soldiers-beat-them-while-they-were-driving-in-west-bank/00000191-c704-df27-a9b9-ff9ea1b00000</link><description>这两个人说，士兵在前往耶路撒冷的途中拦住了他们，命令他们下车，用步枪抵住他们的头，并用枪殴打他们。当他们因受伤要求去医院时，一名士兵威胁说如果他们转身就开枪打死他们</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 12:30:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-06/ty-article/.premium/two-bedouin-israelis-say-idf-soldiers-beat-them-while-they-were-driving-in-west-bank/00000191-c704-df27-a9b9-ff9ea1b00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列法院暂停本-格维尔晋升因对抗议者施暴而接受调查的警官</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-06/ty-article/.premium/court-halts-ben-gvirs-promotion-of-police-officer-accused-of-violence-against-protesters/00000191-c703-de0a-afd5-df4be6440000</link><description>法官裁定，梅厄·苏伊萨的晋升“明显偏离了警方的法律和专业审查程序”。 Suissa 目前正在接受犯罪调查，其中包括向 2023 年反司法改革抗议者投掷眩晕手榴弹</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 11:40:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-06/ty-article/.premium/court-halts-ben-gvirs-promotion-of-police-officer-accused-of-violence-against-protesters/00000191-c703-de0a-afd5-df4be6440000</guid></item><item><title>定居者摧毁了他们的西岸村庄，以色列禁止他们重建它</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-09-06/ty-article-magazine/.premium/settlers-destroyed-their-west-bank-village-israel-forbids-them-from-rebuilding-it/00000191-c24c-de0a-afd5-da4c24d10000</link><description>战争开始时，一个巴勒斯坦社区因担心定居者袭击而放弃了位于南希伯伦山的祖传村庄。以色列法院的裁决允许他们返回，但定居者已经摧毁了他们的大部分房屋。现在军政府不让他们重建</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 11:18:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-09-06/ty-article-magazine/.premium/settlers-destroyed-their-west-bank-village-israel-forbids-them-from-rebuilding-it/00000191-c24c-de0a-afd5-da4c24d10000</guid></item><item><title>随着加沙停火和人质协议濒临崩溃，一个不太可能的步骤可能会使其取得成果</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-06/ty-article/.premium/as-gaza-cease-fire-deal-on-brink-of-collapse-one-unlikely-step-could-bring-it-to-fruition/00000191-c670-df27-a9b9-fffa76690000</link><description>美国将提出最终的“要么接受要么放弃”的提案，这将迫使内塔尼亚胡和哈马斯领导人辛瓦尔决定是否放弃骄傲并妥协。拒绝将大大增加发生地区战争的可能性</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 09:58:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-06/ty-article/.premium/as-gaza-cease-fire-deal-on-brink-of-collapse-one-unlikely-step-could-bring-it-to-fruition/00000191-c670-df27-a9b9-fffa76690000</guid></item><item><title>面对严峻的国内困境，加沙和黎巴嫩的战斗已成为伊朗日益沉重的负担</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-06/ty-article/.premium/faced-with-a-dire-economic-crisis-iran-increasingly-views-the-war-in-gaza-as-a-burden/00000191-c62d-d7cf-a59d-c6ed18320000</link><description>伊朗担心，其与其代理人针对以色列制定的“反应方程式”政策可能会适得其反，将其拖入地区冲突，从而加剧其本已严峻的经济挑战，并阻碍新政府寻求复兴的努力</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 09:41:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-06/ty-article/.premium/faced-with-a-dire-economic-crisis-iran-increasingly-views-the-war-in-gaza-as-a-burden/00000191-c62d-d7cf-a59d-c6ed18320000</guid></item><item><title>以色列计划在联合国教科文组织世界遗产地建立新的西岸定居点，这违反了承诺</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-06/ty-article/.premium/israel-plans-new-w-bank-settlement-at-unesco-world-heritage-site-in-breach-of-commitments/00000191-c669-d76a-a5f1-f66b2f4e0000</link><description>2014年，应巴勒斯坦权力机构的要求，联合国教科文组织将巴蒂尔古代梯田列为世界遗产。尽管以色列七年前退出联合国教科文组织，但它从未放弃在该公约上的签署和承诺</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 09:09:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-06/ty-article/.premium/israel-plans-new-w-bank-settlement-at-unesco-world-heritage-site-in-breach-of-commitments/00000191-c669-d76a-a5f1-f66b2f4e0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯发布被谋杀的以色列裔美国人质赫什·戈德堡-波林的囚禁视频</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-06/ty-article/hamas-publishes-captivity-video-of-murdered-israeli-american-hostage-hersh-goldberg-polin/00000191-c5e1-d86a-a5d7-f5f912400000</link><description>赫什在视频中说，他在加沙幸存下来，几乎没有得到任何医疗护理，而且“不记得上次看到太阳或呼吸新鲜空气是什么时候了。”他的父母表示，这段视频必须立即给世界敲响警钟，要求他们采取行动，确保剩余人质获释。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 06:41:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-06/ty-article/hamas-publishes-captivity-video-of-murdered-israeli-american-hostage-hersh-goldberg-polin/00000191-c5e1-d86a-a5d7-f5f912400000</guid></item></channel></rss>